(302, 'Heads up note 2025-10-18T16:29:00.000+05:30 from @Rahul Mathur: Hi team, Sharing the heads-up note for our investment in [Nimo Planet](https://www.nimoplanet.com/). The company is shipping/fielding spatial computing for work (Core + OS + glasses) Their proposed solution layer is “Nimo Infinity: Personal AI Workspace” — a canvas with “prompt-to-mini-AI apps,” browser agents for legacy apps, sandboxed memory/context, and an MCP app store. DeVC is investing $50K as part of a 700K round @ $5M post money valuation led by [Mucker Capital](https://mucker.com/) Note: Since this is a community top-up to Anand Lalwani; we will be doing deeper work during our November 25 trip to SF where we will spend time with the founder **Founders** 1. [Rohildev Nattukallingal](https://www.linkedin.com/in/rohildev/) 1. 8.5 YOE @ previous startup 1. Had raised ~$3.2M in VC funding (led by Kalaari India) 1. Launch world''s first gesture based wireless smart ring called Neyya 1. [Suneesh Thuluthiyil](/1c829bccb6fc803f8c38fbaa5ef0617f) 1. 8.5 YOE @ previous startup (together) **Investing Process** 1. We were introduced to Rohildev by Anand Lalwani (CoFo @ Cardinal Robotics) who had already committed to invest $50K into the company and is now adding a further $50K 1. Cash did a 1PE - Weak Maybe for Core Cheque 1. *?? Purely technology out and just doesnt seem like a marketable product builder* 1. *?? Not a first principles CX thinker* 1. *?? Lacks growth chops and past history is un-inspiring. Tinkerer sci...')
